---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'January 23, 2026';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Ketamine Software Directory"
  description="Privacy policy for Ketamine Software Directory. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your information."
>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 to-white px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
        Last updated: {lastUpdated}
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none">
        <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <p>
          Ketamine Software Directory ("we," "our," or "us") operates ketaminesoftware.directory. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect information when you visit our website.
        </p>

        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>

        <h3>Information You Provide</h3>
        <p>We may collect information you voluntarily provide, such as:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Email address (when you contact us or subscribe to updates)</li>
          <li>Name and clinic information (when you submit inquiries)</li>
          <li>Any other information you choose to provide via forms or email</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Automatically Collected Information</h3>
        <p>When you visit our site, we may automatically collect:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Browser type and version</li>
          <li>Pages visited and time spent on pages</li>
          <li>Referring website</li>
          <li>General geographic location (country/region level)</li>
          <li>Device type and screen size</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          We use privacy-focused analytics that do not track individual users across websites or use cookies for tracking purposes.
        </p>

        <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use collected information to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Respond to your inquiries and requests</li>
          <li>Improve our website content and user experience</li>
          <li>Understand which content is most useful to visitors</li>
          <li>Send updates if you've subscribed (you can unsubscribe anytime)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Affiliate Links and Third Parties</h2>
        <p>
          Our website contains links to third-party software vendors. When you click these links:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>You will be directed to the vendor's website</li>
          <li>The vendor's privacy policy will apply to your interactions with them</li>
          <li>We may receive a referral commission if you purchase (at no extra cost to you)</li>
          <li>We do not share your personal information with affiliate partners</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          We minimize cookie usage. We do not use advertising cookies or cross-site tracking cookies. Any cookies used are strictly necessary for site functionality or privacy-respecting analytics.
        </p>

        <h2>Data Security</h2>
        <p>
          We implement reasonable security measures to protect your information. However, no internet transmission is completely secure. We encourage you not to share sensitive personal health information via our contact forms.
        </p>

        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Request access to personal information we hold about you</li>
          <li>Request correction or deletion of your information</li>
          <li>Opt out of any marketing communications</li>
          <li>Request we stop processing your information</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@ketaminesoftware.directory">hello@ketaminesoftware.directory</a>.
        </p>

        <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          Our website is not directed at children under 18. We do not knowingly collect information from children.
        </p>

        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. We will post the updated policy on this page with a new "Last updated" date.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Email: <a href="mailto:hello@ketaminesoftware.directory">hello@ketaminesoftware.directory</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
